So I did a project in one laboratory

00:24:42.320 --> 00:24:44.640
and then I did a project
with Liz Blackburn

00:24:45.690 --> 00:24:48.410
on telomeres from unrelated
an unrelated organism,

00:24:48.410 --> 00:24:49.620
and then I did a third project.

00:24:49.620 --> 00:24:51.310
You're not officially allowed

00:24:51.310 --> 00:24:53.950
to make a deal with who
