I knew that I wanted to work with Liz

00:25:00.070 --> 00:25:02.690
during the time that I had
done the rotation with her

00:25:02.690 --> 00:25:04.300
and I knew about this idea,

00:25:05.300 --> 00:25:08.840
how do chromosomes replicate,
how are they maintained,

00:25:08.840 --> 00:25:10.140
and I thought that that was

00:25:10.140 --> 00:25:12.340
the most exciting thing
going on in telomeres.

00:25:12.340 --> 00:25:14.870
So, in May, at the end
